Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Travel Centre 34 provide direct access onto the Pacific Motorway connecting Brisbane and Greater Queensland to the Gold Coast.

- New 10 Year lease to Carl's Jr. An international covenant with over 3,800 restaurants in over 42 countries

- New 10 year lease to Zarraffa's Coffee, an award winning national operator 

- Carl's Jr. & Zarraffa's Coffee have drive thru operations 

- Significant 4,885sqm* land holding on highway location & high growth corridor 

- Brand new improvements providing excellent tax saving depreciation benefits 

- Direct access from the M1 Pacific Motorway for more than 157,000* vehicles per day 

- Strong annual growth by fixed 3% to 4% reviews on a combined net income of $341,660 pa* 

- Complimented by new long term leasing to successful retailers; Liquor Legends and TSG with a combined WALE of 8.74 years* (income)  

To be sold via public auction on Friday 30th November 2018 at 11am (AEST) at the CBRE Head Office Level 3, 1 Eagle Street, Brisbane City.
